{"tid":509073,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"另類「哈韓」? 日本出現北韓粉","createTime":"2017-12-25T01:55:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-25T01:59:09.000Z","uid":161311,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b67b781dc8f5ff865c72cec45a4e337b2afc06b8","tid":509073,"uid":161311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T01:55:08.000Z","msg":"日本近日出現迷上北韓文化的年輕粉絲，他們甚至創建俱樂部，模仿北韓女子團體「牡丹峰樂團」，成立了「先軍少女」穿上自製制服，練習表演「牡丹峰樂團」的歌曲舞蹈，而且觀眾還不少。<br />\n     <br />\n     綜合外媒報導，儘管北韓日前發射2枚飛彈，甚至揚言3個月內擊沉日本，挑釁事件頻傳。但一個名為「東京北韓俱樂部」的團體，卻迷上北韓文化，模仿北韓女子團體「牡丹峰樂團」。<br />\n<br />\n     牡丹峰樂團號稱北韓版的少女時代，成員都由北韓領導人金正恩親自挑選。<br />\n<br />\n    「先軍少女」團長君薰（Chunhun）說，因為大學時研究北韓宣傳技術而著迷於北韓文化，現在為神奈川縣的自由插畫家。<br />\n<br />\n      他說:「我們不支持金正恩的政策，但我們喜歡北韓的音樂和藝術。」在一開始創立俱樂部時的確收到許多保守團體批評，甚至有人質疑「你們在搞反社會活動嗎？」「你是北韓間諜嗎？」但他表示，「就像喜歡美國的泰勒斯或南韓的K-POP一樣，我們喜歡的是北韓文化而已。」<br />\n<br />\n     「先軍少女」的舞蹈和音樂表演也培養了一群粉絲，粉絲甚至會穿上北韓軍裝在台下看表演支持。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2292832\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2292832&d=ELP2qVbdMgDDlt%2FOnKeYKrIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=1d298d42\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2292832&h=96a79ca4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2292832</a>"},{"pid":"8d700d637a0a87418409d82effdd63581d8b23ba","tid":509073,"uid":25858,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T01:56:18.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e4cda72a99a4fd3c8e76ffd48c24ec9f7d168c6","tid":509073,"uid":2096,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T01:58:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/25/095842_d773e6c0e538e7b5eddfd3d74c619ea3.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F25%2F095842_d773e6c0e538e7b5eddfd3d74c619ea3.jpeg&h=61163755&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d6a28025c8681b79cf9f1600e6aa3b2fbc02e06f","tid":509073,"uid":161311,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T01:59:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/25/095719_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F25%2F095719_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=d8b74612&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n個樣好似<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}